WEBVTT

00:00:02.135 --> 00:00:03.873
Wavulana wakubwa hawalii.

00:00:05.217 --> 00:00:06.404
Imezee.

00:00:07.558 --> 00:00:09.392
Kaa kimya na ufutie vumbi juu yake.

00:00:10.462 --> 00:00:13.136
Acha kulia kabla sijakupa
kitu cha kulilia.

00:00:14.258 --> 00:00:16.116
Hizi ni baadhi tu ya vishazi

00:00:16.140 --> 00:00:19.314
vinavyochangia kwenye
ugonjwa ndani ya jamii yetu,

00:00:19.338 --> 00:00:21.297
na hasa zaidi, kwa wanaume wetu.

00:00:22.595 --> 00:00:26.669
Ni ugonjwa uliokuja
kujulikana kama "sumu ya uwanaume."

00:00:28.044 --> 00:00:30.591
Ni moja niliyoteseka kwa kesi sugu,